This game has a racing theme.
Background: Two friends were arguing over who was the fastest, realizing that arueing wouldn't solve any problems, the challenged each other to a race in the park next to the
lake on a brigth sunday afternoon betting that whoever won would have brag rights and new hat. You are attempting to place first in the race. Well you better start stretching 
because themend of the race track is half way across the pond.
